\par 
\par \hich\af32\dbch\af16\loch\f32 Ballack: That could be true. During\hich\af32\dbch\af16\loch\f32 
 the time when Jens was being attacked so fiercely, Timo Hildebrand was also having problems in Valencia. And now, in the 4:0 win over Switzerland, Jens has reinforced his number one position. The trainers also support him, and that's good enough. A goalk
\hich\af32\dbch\af16\loch\f32 e\hich\af32\dbch\af16\loch\f32 eper needs security.
